title: Wall Street Breakfast October 26: What Moved Markets This Week
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Stocks ended the week on an upbeat note, with the S&P 500 finishing just three points shy of its all-time high, after the U.S. Trade Representative's office said Friday it was close to finalizing some sections of a "Phase 1" trade deal with China.
